{"tid":1129633,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★股災？】公司車涉繞道逆線行　前藝人吳啟明「丁旺蟹」認錯：新聘司機唔識路","createTime":"2019-04-28T14:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T05:14:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1040d3a787ea270c30082820d928b2b809b9884","tid":1129633,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/photo/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190428194302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190428194302&h=007c9200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳啟明(左)在電視劇《大時代》飾演「丁旺蟹」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/photo/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190428194302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190428194302&h=b4866e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一部掛有中港車牌的私家車昨晚(27日)疑於中環及灣仔繞道逆線行駛，相關片段在網上流傳引起公眾嘩然，警方暫列「危險駕駛」處理，呼籲目擊者提供資料。東網接獲消息指，涉事車輛後座一位乘客為前藝人吳啟明。吳接受東網訪問時承認，昨晚原定前往中環四季酒店參加圈外朋友舉辦的宴會，未料涉事司機突然逆線駛入繞道，「嚇到我面都青晒」！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190428%2Fbkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001.html&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=96c6cedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190428/bkn-20190428162950492-0428_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b5aa670b592957c51d40bf90736b052f9e216dec","tid":1129633,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=